Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<濑户的花嫁　第6回>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防人之心不可无
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄出击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有永澄屏蔽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张卡我是不会给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了 小巡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你犯规吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张卡是小巡的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能交给任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那张卡就是小巡的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定成为爸爸那样出色的警视总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户流荡 夕阳小浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被救命的 少年永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树立道义 抛开常理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青涩感情 就此开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六话　大小姐 请手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 只是做了一个梦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你生活在独门独院的房子里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经建成三十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你啊 那么现实的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人一上了年纪 不知道会变得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然这么说 好像大叔似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说而已嘛 我只是做了这样一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就代表我们会一直在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都看呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 是妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会让你失望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我做了一个年轻时候的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻姑娘真的这么好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻姑娘真的这么好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这样说 我没有这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻 年轻是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不去回顾 老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 爱是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 就是毫不犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小灿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿 穿围裙的样子也很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有其父必有其子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿 永澄在学校有给你添麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 是我净给永澄添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着这么可爱的妻子 在学校也特别懒散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这一点 我们暂时保密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 我都说不喜欢保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 中学生也有中学生的尴尬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户同学的头发好柔顺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用哪一种洗发水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 盐水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是海水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个海洋深层水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一点痘痘都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 能和大家这么融洽相处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 怎么觉得小灿好像不再是我一人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有一点点焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着小灿傻笑什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小灿关系这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我亲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你们那是什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 那边的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么傻事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巡来教教你们学校的校规吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巡欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 从以前一遇到永澄的事小巡就会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿同学 多说一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听永澄小时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 他们小时候就很要好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人总是在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 他们还组队获得过掀纸牌大赛的冠军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 小学低年级部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矶小大赛二连霸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称矶小掀纸牌皇后 小巡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀纸牌皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起掀纸牌 我就热血沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来一场久违的对决吧 掀纸牌王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人用小学时的外号叫你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有感到过不好意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:09.92,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[掀纸牌之王]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:09.92,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[猿	灿]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:09.92,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[巡	永澄]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 漆黑夜路与逮捕错误
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何 条子的手下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单人囚室 大家一起进去就不恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉起手来 其他的都给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀纸牌好像超级恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因为这种事气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你脸色看起来不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是成为警视总监
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是永澄的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张纸牌是小巡的原则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.65,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[友達：]朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.65,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[クラスメイト：]同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.65,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[私：]我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:29.99,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[友達：]朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:29.99,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[おさな馴染み：]青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你怎么了 小巡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么烦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一看到濑户和永澄在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心就像有警铃在闪烁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种紧急情况还真是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要振作起来 小巡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始要重新打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的 在人行道上要排成两列
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的 上学途中不要打情骂俏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的 不要边玩手机边走路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要小巡教教你们社会规范啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆 啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巡 巡警
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们会从同一间屋子里面出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.61,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[审讯中]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 老实交代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么今早濑户同学会从你家里面走出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 太太 你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满潮同学和濑户同学从同一间屋子里面出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀真讨厌 他们是什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 请对我老公保密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 被抓去审讯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄被逮捕拘留了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说罢 是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 这是有种种原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:10:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健全的中学男女一大早从同一间屋子里出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有正当的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呢 心脏怦怦直跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就说出来听听吧 那个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉一直这样下去也可以 还是不说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪排饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的猪排饭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 我特别想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吃啊 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吃下了那个猪排饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地全部说出来吧 然后就轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我跟小灿是住在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 濑户同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死心了 你逮捕我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄同小灿是亲戚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗 那你的父亲是做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在用古老的拷问刑具审问永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的小子跟小灿住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能原谅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来濑户老师是小灿的父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓氏一样 我就在想不会是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 你母亲现在在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加一块
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚捅了父亲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全家人都来学校了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲做孩子的班主任没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到校长的许可了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户同学到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户老师他们也住永澄家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为家庭原因 父亲他们住在别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然和濑户同学住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿被水淋到了 会被人类发现真实身份的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你擦脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起 濑户同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么做作地抱住她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户同学 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.35,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[親娘：]母女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.35,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[親娘：]父女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.35,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[親バカ：]溺爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.35,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[夫婦：]夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:06.58,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[親娘：]母女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:06.58,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[尾びれ：]尾鳍 人类?or鱼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:06.58,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[親バカ：]溺爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:06.58,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[夫婦：]夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底是怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡这家伙 昨天的样子好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会看到小灿的脚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照人鱼的规定 要是向人类暴露了真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人鱼或人中的一个就会被杀掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后 她上课的样子和平时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一般会认为那是眼睛的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说濑户同学被水淋到的话脚会发生什么变化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露馅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢 小巡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为会弄湿小灿 我才挡住了她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了 濑户同学的脚变成鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这种妄想而对人泼水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不正常哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能认为我说的话很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 小巡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了你好 就不要再追问了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 从江户时代起我家代代都是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那血告诉我 濑户同学绝对有什么古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在变成确信了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 点燃了小巡的巡警斗志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是仁侠什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归根到底 黑道是见不得人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:33.16,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[哭给你看]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被巡警盯上是宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿也进入仁侠模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的一切都很不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在起她有什么不自然的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都别想从我的眼下逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户同学 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水开得太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 不小心绊到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.19,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[女厕所]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手不听使唤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉 永澄是男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男的为什么会出现在女厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄一直跟踪小灿到女生厕所还偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 不能在学校用刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 放学了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿大小姐 灿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在窥探灿大小姐的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为灿小姐的护卫 我来解决那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不确定一定暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大又开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄是为了保护小巡才那么努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为妻子 我也要尽全力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:16:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不只是为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小巡真的知道了真相 可能会被灭口的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户同学这么彻底地避开沾水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然难以置信 但她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡警
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实是鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真可惜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算装作不知道 对我钱形巡也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫最喜欢鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗得过人 你能骗得过猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巡 你好像笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:42.95,shangmian,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果超群
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还不止一只哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围攻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人鱼的武器是声音 用尖啸之音干掉猫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 巡警和猿同学看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然避开我过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的都聚集过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然如此受欢迎 不愧是小灿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿大小姐 那个人我会处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 赶快用尖啸之音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想破坏包括小巡在内的现在的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被猫咬到也不能使用人鱼的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巡 你到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为好奇心去挖掘别人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小灿对你做了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她给谁添麻烦了吗
